item.title: Hey guys
item.dc:creator: @Swift1 Swift`
item.description:
@Swift1 wrote:

Changing Client Name

If you mean ‘change the client name’ as in the name displayed on the title bar then it’s in Frame_Sub1.java. I don’t think I really need to explain that.

Moving NPCs
You configure an NPCs movement through your autospawn.cfg.
It uses the format:

//------NpcID---CoordX--CoordY--Height--RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType

RangeX1 = The X Coord of the East Direction
RangeY1 = The Y Coord of the North Direction
RangeX2 = The X Coord of the West Direction
RangeY2 = The Y Coord of the South Direction
